collection.name: JunkYardDogs
collection.description:
"Welcome to the JunkYard! We've got scrap and flames!"

JYD members get exclusive access to private channels in our Discord as well as future perks including Airdrops, Sandbox access, exclusive member-only merch drops and more.  The strongest aspect of the project is that community and becoming part of the JYD fam.  Join the pack!

Remember, your dog is YOURS. You've got 100% commercial rights to your dog as long as it's in your wallet!  Have fun! With great power comes great responsibility!  Check our TOS at https://JunkYardDogs.io/tos

We are the JunkYard Dogs, and this is where our story begins.
